                Pa<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>My dear Sir<lb/></p>
            <p>There will be examination of<lb/> new applicants for sepher class Monday and the<lb/> class will be opened next day.  Dr Kohut&#44; Wise and I were present<lb/> last Tuesday.  Frommser came to see me&#59; he is much downhearted.<lb/>  What is your custom as to &#91;Hebrew&#93; in synagogue when there is a &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/> but the &#91;Hebrew&#93; is not in synagogue&#63;  What is the custom in<lb/> London&#63;  Does it make any difference if the &#91;Hebrew&#93; present<lb/> and not the &#91;Hebrew&#93;&#63;  Dr Kohut is about to send out those circulars in<lb/> his congregation.<lb/>  Good Shabat.<lb/> Yrs<lb/> H. Pereira Mendes<lb/> 27 W 16.<lb/></p>
            </body>
